descript.abstract: Major Lakes (layer) is a symbolized and labeled display presentation of the World lakes data set. The geographic and attribute data World lakes are symbolized and labeled to create the layer. All features are symbolized as a single symbol. Features are labeled based on the NAME attribute.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
